1980;;Phobia;;Canadian;;John Huston;;Paul Michael Glaser, Susan Hogan, John Colicos, Patricia Collins;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phobia_(1980_film);;Psychiatrist Dr. Peter Ross (Glaser) M.D., is using radical techniques on his patients to cure them of their various phobias. He becomes terrified when someone starts murdering the subjects one at a time.